[SN]TITLE[SN]
In pictures: The Scottish Street Food Awards

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
More than a dozen food trucks have taken part in the inaugural Scottish Street Food Awards at The Pitt in Edinburgh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Two entrants made it through to the British awards to be held in Manchester in September.
The public vote winner was urban seafood seller ShrimpWreck, while fried chicken specialist The Buffalo Truck was crowned champion by a panel of top chefs.
